speech: Sorry, I didn't understand what you are saying . You can say 'New Order' or 'Track Order'.                                                                                                                                   Also, in a new order, please mention only items from our available menu: Koshari, Tamiya, Hamam Mahshi, Mulukhiyah, Feteer Meshaltet, Hawawshi, Kanafeh, Umm Ali, Basbousa and Samosa.                                                                                               Also specify a quantity for each item for example: "One Koshari and 2 Hawawshi"
